---
layout: layout.njk
title: Salary Guides for Tech Roles
metaTitle: "Tech Salary Guides | Askia Blog"
metaDescription: "Structured tech salary guides for DevOps, SRE, platform, and cloud roles built to help candidates understand bands, leverage, and negotiation angles."
breadcrumbs:
  - name: "Home"
    url: "/"
  - name: "Resources"
    url: "/resources/"
  - name: "Career Intelligence"
    url: "/blog/"
  - name: "Salary Guides"
    url: "/blog/salary/"
---
<section class="blog-hero">
  <div class="container blog-hero-grid">
    <div class="blog-hero-copy">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Compensation Mastery</p>
      <h1 class="blog-hero-title">Salary Guides Inside the Blog</h1>
      <p class="blog-hero-subtitle">Structured pay guides for technical roles, designed as a searchable blog sublibrary instead of another flat pile of posts.</p>
      <div class="blog-hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/salary-negotiation/">Get Salary Negotiation Help</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/blog/interview/">Browse Interview Guides</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-hero-media">
      <div class="blog-hero-image">
        <img src="/assets/blog/offer-range.jpg" alt="Career compensation planning visuals." loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
        <span class="holo-badge">PAY SIGNAL</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section blog-grid-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="blog-grid">
      {% for post in blogSalaryPages | reverse %}
      <article class="blog-card">
        <a class="blog-card-image" href="/blog/salary/{{ post.slug }}/">
          <img src="{{ post.featuredImage }}" alt="{{ post.imageAlt }}" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
        <div class="blog-card-body">
          <div class="blog-card-meta">
            {% for category in post.categories %}
              <span class="category-pill">{{ category }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          <h2><a href="/blog/salary/{{ post.slug }}/">{{ post.title }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ post.description }}</p>
          <div class="blog-card-foot">
            <span>{{ post.readTime }}</span>
            <span>{{ post.publishDate }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% set featuredMarketsTitle = "Markets with strong compensation intent" %}
{% set featuredMarketsSubtitle = "These city pages support the compensation library with local-market context, role targeting, and stronger conversion paths." %}
{% include "featured-markets.njk" %}

<script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "CollectionPage",
    "name": "Askia Salary Guides",
    "description": "Structured salary guides for technical roles covering compensation bands, leverage, and negotiation context.",
    "url": "{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}"
  }
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "name": "Salary guide pages",
    "itemListElement": [
      {% for post in blogSalaryPages | reverse %}
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": {{ loop.index }},
        "name": "{{ post.title }}",
        "url": "{{ site.url }}/blog/salary/{{ post.slug }}/"
      }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    ]
  }
</script>
